professional productivity and security. The 13th-generation Intel Core i7-1355U processor, with up to 4.6 GHz using Intel Turbo Boost Technology, offers quick performance. It’s complemented with 8GB of DDR4-3200MHz RAM and a fast 512GB PCIe NVMe SSD. The HP ProBook 440 G10’s 14″ FHD IPS display with minimal bezels and anti-glare coating produces crisp visuals at 250 nits brightness, making it perfect for work and entertainment consumption. This laptop is extremely lightweight, weighing only 1.38 kg and measuring 32.19 x 21.39 x 1.99 cm. It includes the HP Premium Keyboard, which is spill-resistant and illuminated for better usage. The HP Long Life 3-cell, 51 Wh Li-ion battery allows for longer use, while Intel Wi-Fi 6E AX211 and Bluetooth 5.3 offer seamless connectivity. HP Cloud Recovery and the HP Client Management Script Library are two management features. Security is prioritized with features such as HP Sure Click, HP Sure Sense, and the inbuilt TPM 2.0 security chip. The Laptop also has a fingerprint sensor for additional biometric security. The HP ProBook 440 G10 is not only a powerhouse for professionals, but it also promotes sustainability by using low-halogen materials, recycled plastic, and ocean-bound plastic in its design. This laptop’s quality look and sturdy features make it a dependable choice for corporate customers.

detail.name: Lenovo LOQ AI Powered Gaming (9) (83GS006LLK) 12th Gen Core-i5 16GB RAM 512GB SSD RTX 2050 Gaming Laptop

details.description_text: Processor: 12th Gen Intel Core i5-12450HX Memory: 16GB (2x8GB) DDR5 Storage: 512GB M.2 PCIe 4.0 NVMe SSD GPU: NVIDIA RTX 2050 4GB GDDR6 Display: 15.6-inch Full HD (1920x1080) Experience the ultimate gaming experience with the Lenovo LOQ Gaming (83GS006LLK) 12th Gen Core-i5 Gaming Laptop. It is powered by the 12th Gen Intel Core i5-12450HX Processor that provides 8-Cores (4 P-cre + 4 E-core) / 12 Threads, up to 4.4GHz max boost with a 12MB cache. This powerful processor provides seamless multitasking capabilities, also can handle even the most demanding games and applications with ease. Equipped with an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2050 4GB GDDR6 graphics card with boost clock 1575MHz, and TGP 65W, which provides lifelike visuals, ray tracing, and smooth frame rates. So, gamers can enjoy an ultimate gaming experience. This Lenovo LOQ Gaming Laptop comes with the latest dual-channel DDR5 16GB (2x 8GB) 4800 Bus SO-DIMM memory, which is also upgradeable up to 32GB. It has a 512GB M.2 2242 PCIe 4.0x4 NVMe SSD that delivers the highest performance and fastest response times for all workloads. This Lenovo LOQ Gaming Laptop comes with a 15.6-inch Full HD (1920x1080) 300nits brightness 144Hz refresh rate IPS display. This display comes with many features such as Anti-glare and G-SYNC.For long-term backup, this laptop is integrated with an Integrated 60Wh battery. With this large amount of battery capacity, gamers can enjoy marathon gaming sessions without the need for frequent recharging breaks. For better wireless connectivity it has the latest Wi-Fi 6, 11ax 2x2, and Bluetooth 5.2 Wireless Card. Also, it has Integrated 100/1000M (RJ-45) LAN connectivity. So, users can experience seamless gaming and smoother video streaming. It has a variety of ports, including 3x USB-A (USB 5Gbps / USB 3.2 Gen 1), 1x USB-C (USB 10Gbps / USB 3.2 Gen 2), with Lenovo PD 140W and DisplayPort 1.4, 1x HDMI 2.1, up to 8K/60Hz, 1x Headphone/microphone combo jack (3.5mm), 1x Ethernet (RJ-45) and 1x Power connector.The HD 720p with E-shutter webcam is ideal for live-streaming, video conferences, and online classes. This laptop comes with Stereo speakers, 2W x2, optimized with Nahimic Gaming Audio system that provides a stunning audio experience. This laptop comes with a White Backlit, English (EU) keyboard that helps in low-light areas. The Trusted Platform Module (TPM) provides security against threats like firmware and ransomware attacks. The genuine Windows 11 Home Single Language, English is preloaded on this laptop. The Luna Grey of this laptop offers a sleek and stylish look. Box content includes a Lenovo LOQ Gaming (83GS006LLK) Gaming Laptop, 135W Slim Tip (3-pin) power adapter, and user manuals. For peace of mind, Lenovo provides a 2-year brand warranty on laptops and a 1-year warranty on power adapters.

details.description_text: 13th Gen Intel Core i5-13420H Processor (up to 4.60 GHz, 8 Cores) NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 6GB GDDR6 Dedicated Graphics 16GB DDR5 RAM, 512GB PCIe Gen4 SSD 15.6-inch FHD (1920 x 1080) 144Hz Anti-glare Display Advanced cooling system with dual fans Full-size backlit keyboard Versatile connectivity: USB-C, USB-A, HDMI, RJ-45, Audio Combo Jack Pre-installed Windows 11 Home Durable Storm Grey chassis, 2.4 kg The Lenovo LOQ Gaming 9 83DV00F9LK is engineered to deliver outstanding gaming and multitasking performance. Equipped with the latest 13th Gen Intel Core i5-13420H processor and 16GB DDR5 RAM, this laptop offers fast processing speed for the most demanding games and creative applications. Featuring an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 6GB dedicated graphics card, you’ll enjoy smooth and immersive visuals, making every gaming session truly engaging. Its 15.6-inch Full HD display with a high 144Hz refresh rate and anti-glare technology ensures stunning clarity and fluid motion, perfect for both competitive gaming and entertainment. The 512GB PCIe Gen4 SSD provides rapid boot times and ample storage for your games and files. Stay connected with a comprehensive array of input/output ports, including USB-C, USB-A, HDMI, RJ-45 for wired networking, and an audio combo jack. The full-size backlit keyboard enhances your gaming experience, especially in low-light environments. Housed in a robust Storm Grey chassis and weighing 2.4 kg, the Lenovo LOQ Gaming 9 balances performance, durability, and style, making it an excellent choice for gamers and power users on the go.

detail.name: Lenovo LOQ 15IRX9 AI-Powered Gaming (83DV00V0LK) 13th Gen Core i7-13650HX 16GB RAM 1TB SSD RTX 4050 15.6-inch FHD Gaming Laptop

details.description_text: Certifications: MIL-STD-810H military Test Passed Processor: Intel Core i7-13650HX RAM & Storage: 16GB SO-DIMM DDR5-4800 Memory, 1TB M.2 PCIe 4.0x4 NVMe SSD Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4050 6GB GDDR6 Display: 15.6" Full HD (1920x1080) Experience the ultimate gaming experience with the Lenovo LOQ 15IRX9 AI-Powered Gaming (83DV00V0LK) 13th Gen Core i7-13650HX 16GB RAM 1TB SSD RTX 4050 15.6-inch FHD Gaming Laptop. It is powered by the 13th Gen Intel Core i7-13650HX Processor that provides 14-Cores (8 P-cores + 12 E-cores) / 20 Threads, up to 4.9GHz max boost with a 24MB cache. This powerful processor provides seamless multitasking capabilities and can easily handle even the most demanding games and applications. Equipped with an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4050 6GB GDDR6 graphics card with Boost Clock 2370MHz, TGP 105W, and 194 AI TOPS, which provides lifelike visuals, ray tracing, and smooth frame rates. So, gamers can enjoy an ultimate gaming experience. This Lenovo LOQ Gaming Laptop comes with the latest dual-channel DDR5 1x 16GB 4800 Bus SO-DIMM memory, which is upgradeable up to 32 GB. It has a 1TB M.2 2242 PCIe 4.0x4 NVMe SSD that delivers the highest performance and fastest response times for all workloads. This Lenovo LOQ Gaming Laptop comes with a 15.6-inch Full HD (1920x1080), 300nits brightness, 144Hz refresh rate IPS display. This display comes with many features, such as Anti-glare.For long-term backup, this laptop is integrated with an Integrated 60Wh battery. With this large battery capacity, gamers can enjoy marathon gaming sessions without the need for frequent recharging breaks. For better wireless connectivity, it has the latest Wi-Fi 6, 802.11ax 2x2, and Bluetooth 5.2 Wireless Card. Also, it has 100/1000M (RJ-45) LAN connectivity. So, users can experience seamless gaming and smoother video streaming. It has a variety of ports, including 3x USB-A (USB 5Gbps / USB 3.2 Gen 1), 1x USB-C (USB 10Gbps / USB 3.2 Gen 2), with Lenovo PD 140W and DisplayPort 1.4, 1x HDMI 2.1, up to 8K/60Hz, 1x Headphone/microphone combo jack (3.5mm), 1x Ethernet (RJ-45), 1x Power connector.The HD 720p with E Shutter webcam is ideal for live streaming, video conferences, and online classes. This laptop comes with Stereo speakers, 2W x2, optimized with a Nahimic Audio system that provides a stunning audio experience. This laptop comes with a White Backlit keyboard, English (EU), which helps in low-light areas. The Firmware TPM 2.0 Enabled provides security against threats like firmware and ransomware attacks. The genuine Windows 11 Home Single Language, English, is preloaded on this laptop. The Luna Grey of this laptop offers a sleek and stylish look. Box content includes a Lenovo LOQ 15IRX9 AI-Powered Gaming (83DV00V0LK) Gaming Laptop, a 170W Slim Tip (3-pin) power adapter, and user manuals. For peace of mind, Lenovo provides a 2-year brand warranty on laptops and a 1-year warranty on power adapters.

details.description_text: Certification: MIL-STD-810H military test passed Processor: Intel Core i5-13450HX RAM & Storage: 16GB DDR5 Memory, 512GB M.2 PCIe 4.0x4 NVMe SSD Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 6GB GDDR6 Display: 15.6-inch Full HD (1920 x 1080) The Lenovo LOQ Gaming 9 83DV00HKLK is engineered for serious gamers and demanding users, delivering next-level performance with its cutting-edge hardware. Powered by the 13th Gen Intel Core i5-13420H processor and paired with the latest NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4050 6GB GDDR6 graphics, this laptop ensures smooth gameplay and rapid multitasking. The immersive 15.6-inch FHD IPS display features a high 144Hz refresh rate and 350 nits brightness, offering crisp visuals and fluid motion for an exceptional gaming experience. With 16GB DDR5 RAM and a 512GB PCIe Gen4 SSD, both speed and storage space are optimized for quick load times and seamless operation. Advanced cooling, thanks to Lenovo’s LA1 AI chip and dual-fan system, keeps the system running efficiently even during intense gaming sessions. Additional features like a 4-zone RGB backlit keyboard, robust connectivity including Wi-Fi 6 and Bluetooth 5.1, and a solid 60Wh battery with Rapid Charge make this gaming laptop as versatile as it is powerful. The LOQ Gaming 9 is pre-installed with Windows 11 Home, making it ready for both work and play right out of the box.

Powered by the Intel Core i3-1215U processor, which features a 10M cache and can reach speeds up to 4.40 GHz, this laptop ensures smooth performance for everyday computing tasks such as web browsing, word processing, and multimedia consumption. It comes equipped with 8GB of DDR4 RAM, providing adequate memory for multitasking and allowing users to run multiple applications simultaneously without significant slowdowns. With a resolution of 1366 x 768, the 15.6-inch HD display offers bright, clear images that are appropriate for both work and pleasure. Despite not being Full HD, the display is good enough for most daily tasks. The laptop has many ports for connection, including a Type-C connector for quicker data transmission and more flexible networking choices. Additionally, an HD camera is included, allowing high-video-quality participation in virtual meetings and video conferences. Because of its lightweight and small design, the HP 250 G9 is ideal for professionals and students who are always on the go. The HP 250 G9 Core i3 12th Gen 15.6″ HD Laptop strikes a balance between affordability and functionality, making it an excellent choice for those needing a reliable machine for everyday tasks. product_name: ASUS TUF Gaming A15 FA506NFR-HN004W Ryzen 7 7435HS 8GB RAM 512GB SSD RTX 2050 GPU Gaming Laptop

detail.name: ASUS TUF Gaming A15 FA506NFR-HN004W Ryzen 7 7435HS 8GB RAM 512GB SSD RTX 2050 GPU Gaming Laptop

details.description_text: Processor: AMD Ryzen 7 7435HS RAM: 8GB DDR5 Storage: 512GB PCIe 4.0 NVMe M.2 SSD Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2050 4GB GDDR6 GPU Display: 15.6-inch Full HD (1920 x 1080) Experience the ultimate gaming experience with the ASUS TUF Gaming A15 FA506NFR-HN004W Ryzen 7 7435HS 8GB RAM 512GB SSD RTX 2050 GPU Gaming Laptop. It is powered by the latest AMD Ryzen 7 7435HS Mobile Processor that provides 8 Cores and 16 Threads, up to 4.5 GHz max boost with a 20MB cache. This powerful processor provides seamless multitasking capabilities, also can handle even the most demanding games and applications with ease. It is equipped with an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2050 4GB GDDR6 Laptop GPU with Up to 1670MHz at 60W (70W with Dynamic Boost), which provides lifelike visuals, ray tracing, and smooth frame rates. So, gamers can enjoy an ultimate gaming experience. This ASUS TUF Gaming A15 Gaming Laptop comes with the latest DDR5 8GB 5600 Bus speed SO-DIMM memory, which is upgradeable up to 32GB. It has a 512GB PCIe 4.0 NVMe M.2 SSD that delivers the highest performance and fastest response times for all workloads. This gaming laptop has an extra SSD to update your storage capacity further. This ASUS TUF Gaming A15 Gaming Laptop comes with a 15.6-inch FHD (1920 x 1080) 16:9 aspect ratio with 250nits brightness and 144Hz refresh rate Value IPS-level display with Adaptive-Sync Technology providing crisp visual and fast gameplay experience.For long-term backup, this laptop is integrated with a 48WHrs, 3S1P, 3-cell Li-ion battery that Recharges from 0-50% in 30 minutes. With this large amount of battery capacity, gamers can enjoy marathon gaming sessions without the need for frequent recharging breaks. It has the latest Wi-Fi 6(802.11ax) (Dual band) 2*2 and Bluetooth 5.3 Wireless Card (*Bluetooth version may change with OS version different.) for better wireless connectivity. Also, it has 10/100/1000 Mbps LAN connectivity. So, users can experience seamless gaming and smoother video streaming. It has a variety of ports, including 1x HDMI 2.1 TMDS, 3x USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type-A, 1x 3.5mm Combo Audio Jack, 1x USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-C support DisplayPort and 1x RJ45 LAN port.The 720P HD camera is ideal for live streaming, video conferences, and online classes. This laptop has a 2-speaker system featuring AI noise-canceling technology, DTS software and Hi-Res certification (for headphones) that provides a stunning audio experience. This laptop comes with a Backlit Chiclet Keyboard 1-Zone RGB that helps in low-light areas. The genuine Windows 11 Home is preloaded on this laptop. The Graphite Black of this laptop offers a sleek and stylish look. Box content includes an ASUS TUF Gaming A15 FA506NFR-HN004W Gaming Laptop, ø6.0, 150W AC Adapter, and user manuals. For peace of mind, Asus provides a 2-year brand warranty on laptops and a 1-year battery warranty.

detail.name: Lenovo LOQ 15IRX9 – 13th Gen Intel Core i7‑13650HX, 16 GB DDR5 RAM, 512 GB NVMe SSD, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4060 (8 GB), 15.6″ FHD 144 Hz Gaming Laptop

details.description_text: Powerful 14th Gen Intel Core i7 HX processor with 14 cores (6 Performance + 8 Efficiency) and turbo up to 4.9 GHz Dedicated NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4060 graphics with 8GB GDDR6 VRAM for smooth gaming and creative work 16GB DDR5-4800 MHz RAM in dual-channel (2×8GB), expandable for future needs Fast 512GB PCIe 4.0 NVMe SSD with an extra M.2 slot for additional storage Stunning 15.6″ Full HD (1920×1080) IPS antiglare display with 144Hz refresh rate and 100% sRGB color coverage AI-optimized cooling system and dual fans keep performance stable under heavy load Modern design with durable build (MIL-STD-810H), RGB backlit keyboard and privacy shutter webcam Wide connectivity: USB-C (Power Delivery & DisplayPort), multiple USB-A ports, HDMI 2.1, RJ-45 LAN, audio combo jack The Lenovo LOQ 15IRX9 combines desktop-level gaming performance and smart design in a portable chassis. Powered by the Intel Core i7‑13650HX—a 14-core processor—it delivers fast single-thread performance for gaming and multi-thread efficiency for streaming or content creation. Its AI-tuned cooling system ensures sustained performance under load.Featuring 16 GB of DDR5 RAM, expandable up to 32 GB, and a blazing 512 GB PCIe 4.0 SSD, with room for a second SSD, this setup is both powerful and future-proof. The RTX 4060 GPU (8 GB) delivers high-frame-rate gaming, supported by a vibrant 144 Hz FHD IPS display with G‑SYNC to eliminate screen tearing.Despite its high-end internals, the laptop remains durable—MIL‑STD‑810H certified—and still under 2.4 kg. Gamers will appreciate the RGB keyboard, privacy webcam shutter, and refined Nahimic audio experience. I/O options include fast-charging USB‑C, multiple USB‑A ports, HDMI 2.1, and wired Ethernet. A 60 Wh battery with rapid charge keeps you powered for long sessions. Altogether, it's a well-rounded choice for gamers and creators seeking performance and portability.
